{"tid":2378992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 釋出〈Celebrity〉MV 預告片！每一幕都美不勝收","createTime":"2021-01-25T02:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T12:45:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":71,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a458ef0f0bc67c1529f8155d1f82b7b6ec13bc01","tid":2378992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_2819ae0c432588580185742d55dc9890/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-25/133244-894678.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_2819ae0c432588580185742d55dc9890%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-25%2F133244-894678.png&h=eb6df363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再過兩天，IU 就會發行正規五輯中的先行曲，大家應該都等不及了吧？<br />\n<br />\nEDAM Entertainment 今天（25 日）零點首度公開 IU 新專輯先行曲 &ldquo;Celebrity&rdquo; 的 MV 預告片，雖然只有短短不到半分鐘，但影片由多幕華麗的場景組成，一公開立刻掀起熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wQ_ZQwdXRII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwQ_ZQwdXRII&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCKcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=1be1d64d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wQ_ZQwdXRII</a><br />\n<br />\n在精心打造的佈景中，IU 搭配著重複行進的明確旋律，一口氣展現了多種面貌，以變化多端的造型和場景設計，堆疊出令人迫不及待的豐富層次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_31a5b9e4bd7b45fad6c9f7ef5aae99c5/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-25/133244-894677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_31a5b9e4bd7b45fad6c9f7ef5aae99c5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-25%2F133244-894677.jpg&h=2121c3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_faaebd1f23b9cf40bd42a7aba3416916/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-25/133244-894679.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_faaebd1f23b9cf40bd42a7aba3416916%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-25%2F133244-894679.jpg&h=5977bd11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Celebrity&rdquo; 有著 IU 首度嘗試、開朗輕快的 Pop 風格，將為她的第五張正規專輯打頭陣，大家別忘了在 27 日傍晚 6 點（韓國時間）準時鎖定音源和 MV 囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：EDAM Entertainment）"},{"pid":"57631bf27d488e2565ad2c3d618ca09504693990","tid":2378992,"uid":93096,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:44:01.000Z","msg":"iu勁癲..."},{"pid":"63bb4f828ed0eaef1e96fe315c394a81b29972de","tid":2378992,"uid":229026,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會太靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61846622bb87ec7227922cf6996b9131f9067197","tid":2378992,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63bb4f828ed0eaef1e96fe315c394a81b29972de","tid":2378992,"uid":229026,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會太靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:45:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會太癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c127d22721cc31143fd9f824b230934f21cbe9c","tid":2378992,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57631bf27d488e2565ad2c3d618ca09504693990","tid":2378992,"uid":93096,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:44:01.000Z","msg":"iu勁癲..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:45:55.000Z","msg":"iu勁仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d1523d1a7de3c743597e65cfbb08e5f6185144","tid":2378992,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61846622bb87